# ---- Third-party dataset (Abridge, synthetic; committed so teammates can run
# against real records — the performedPeriod class of bug only shows up there).
# Fully synthetic per its README: Synthea patients, LLM-generated transcripts,
# no real patient data. Provided by Abridge for hackathon use; no LICENSE ships
# with it, so keep it to the data files only.
# index.html is a 2M standalone browser viewer — redundant in a repo.
data/abridge/synthetic-ambient-fhir-25/index.html
data/abridge/**/*.zip
